                  </hi>. I live in Robert-street, Bedford-row. At five o'clock in the afternoon of the 21st of Aug., I was going throngh a crowd in St. Giles's—I felt something at my pocket—I immediately missed my handkerchief—I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184308210196"></xptr>
               <p>turned, and saw the prisoner—I caught hold of him, and accused him—he said he had not had it—he attempted to get away—I saw the corner of my handkerchief out of his pocket—I laid hold of it—the policeman came up and took it and the prisoner—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How far was I from you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About a yard and a half.</p>
